<plot>A documentary made by students of the First Television School at Rhodes University, South Africa, The Story of Albany Farm chronicles the true account of a farm attack on Peter Wylie and the killing of his elderly father. The film recreates the actual attack and one man's extraordinary response to the crime.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?593603</url></doc>
